        "action": "Advise people to avoid shaking hands during COVID-19",
        "additional_details": "Similar to the advice to sing \u2018Happy Birthday\u2019 advice during hand washing, we could ask everyone to give the \u2018Royal Nod\u2019 with a smile, as a simple way of greeting people instead of shaking hands.\r\n \r\nSave lives, show national solidarity during crisis and be helpful.",
